# Day 5 – Python Dictionaries 📚

## What it does
Explores Python dictionaries using a real-world
example — a student profile with nested lists.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3 (built-in only)

## How to run
python dictionary.py

## What I learned
- Creating dictionaries with key-value pairs
- Storing lists as dictionary values
- Accessing and printing dictionary data

## Output
Prints a structured student profile dictionary.
